Greetings!

We're happy to announce that BGS and Boards and Brews (BnB) are having a collaborative membership! 

*Currently* only available for BGS club members, you may apply for a BnBxBGS membership for RM20/yr

This is a tier based promotion, meaning for every 20 BGS members who sign up, everyone levels up a tier on promotions.

Tier 1 (1-19 BnBxBGD members): 
10% off F&B  orders 

Tier 2 (20-39 BnBxBGS members): Free entry to BnB every Thursdays! _meaning you don't have to fight for the first 15 spots_

Tier 3: TBA

Just present your BGS membership card and serial number to BnB registration counter, pay RM20 for the BnB membership and done! you get to enjoy the promo!

[Ready, Set, Go!🎲]
.
🌙 Have you ever heard of “Game Therapy”? Game therapy is an emotional intervention that may help you to build a positive mindset and actions through playing games, socializing and reflection! 
.
🌙 This February, Sunway Peer Counselling Volunteers (PCV) will be collaborating with Sunway Board Games Society (BGS) to hold a game therapy session, titled Ready, Set, Go! Various interesting board games will be played such as Exploding Kittens, Codenames, Coup, and another mystery game that will only be revealed on the event day itself. 😉
.
🌙There will be three parts in this session; in the first part we will have three different games stations available for you, next we will be playing a team based game and finally we will end with a reflection.
.
🌙 By joining this fun board game session, you will be able to gain a positive mind while bonding with your new friends! Do invite your peers along to have an exciting board games night~ Scan the QR code or visit the link in our bio to register.
.
